<div style="--color-primary:#FF6B6B;--color-secondary:#4ECDC4;--font-primary:Abhaya Libre;--font-secondary:Inter" data-sr-theme=""><div class="announcement-modal" style="background-color:#FF6B6B;color:#FFFFFF;padding:30px;border-radius:12px;text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:20px auto;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.2)" data-sr-id="announcement-modal"><h2 style="font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:15px;color:#FFFFFF;font-family:var(--font-primary), serif">✨ New Braiding Classes at Crown of Beauty! ✨</h2><div class="rich-text-content" style="margin-bottom:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#FFFFFF"><p>We're <strong>excited</strong> to announce that we're now offering braiding classes for all skill levels! Whether you're looking to master the basics or elevate your styling game, we've got a class for you:</p></div><ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:15px 0"><li style="padding:8px 0;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;color:#FFFFFF">• <!-- -->Braids &amp; Twist</li><li style="padding:8px 0;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;color:#FFFFFF">• <!-- -->Designs</li><li style="padding:8px 0;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;color:#FFFFFF">• <!-- -->Cornrows</li><li style="padding:8px 0;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;color:#FFFFFF">• <!-- -->Extension Braids</li></ul><p style="margin-top:15px;font-weight:600;font-size:1.1rem;font-style:italic;color:#FFFFFF">Interested? Call us to inquire about pricing and book your lessons today!</p></div><nav class="navigation-bar" style="position:relative;background:var(--color-primary);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-secondary);z-index:1000;width:100%" data-sr-id="nav"><div class="banner-bar" style="background-color:#FF6B6B;color:#FFFFFF;padding:8px 0;text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);width:100%" data-sr-id="banner"><div class="banner-content rich-text-content" style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;font-family:var(--font-secondary, Inter