l your needs. We offer a <strong>wide range</strong> of professional treatments tailored to you.</p></div><div class="services-menu" style="font-family:var(--font-secondary), Arial, sans-serif;width:100%;padding:20px 0 40px 0"><div class="service-tabs" style="display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:20px;flex-wrap:wrap"><div class="service-tab active" data-service-type="Hair" style="padding:12px 24px;background-color:var(--color-secondary);color:#000;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid #000">Hair</div><div class="service-tab" data-service-type="Facial" style="padding:12px 24px;background-color:var(--color-primary);color:white;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid #000">Facial</div><div class="service-tab" data-service-type="Nails" style="padding:12px 24px;background-color:var(--color-primary);color:white;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid #000">Nails</div></div><div class="service-content active" id="content-Hair" style="display:block;background:white;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:4px;padding:50px 20px;width:100%"><h2 class="service-section-title" style="text-align:center;color:var(--color-primary);font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:25px;margin-top:0">Hair<!-- --> &amp; Services</h2><div class="services-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px 40px;width:100%;padding:20px"><div class="service-item" style="padding-bottom:12px"><div class="service-header" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;position:relative"><span class="service-name-wrapper" style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:5px;flex:1;min-width:0"><span class="service-name" style="font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:#333">Hair Cut</span></span><span class="service-price" style="text-align:right;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-primary);font-size:15px;white-space:nowrap;background:white;padding-left:8px">$50.00</span></div><div class="service-description" style="color:#666;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;margin-top:3