style="color:#666;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;margin-top:3px;text-align:left;font-family:var(--font-secondary), Arial, sans-serif">Rejuvenating facial treatment</div></div></div></div><div class="service-content" id="content-Nails" style="display:none;background:white;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:4px;padding:50px 20px;width:100%"><h2 class="service-section-title" style="text-align:center;color:var(--color-primary);font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:25px;margin-top:0">Nails<!-- --> &amp; Services</h2><div class="services-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px 40px;width:100%;padding:20px"><div class="service-item" style="padding-bottom:12px"><div class="service-header" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;position:relative"><span class="service-name-wrapper" style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:5px;flex:1;min-width:0"><span class="service-name" style="font-weight:600;font-size:15px;color:#333">Manicure</span></span><span class="service-price" style="text-align:right;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-primary);font-size:15px;white-space:nowrap;background:white;padding-left:8px">$35.00</span></div><div class="service-description" style="color:#666;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;margin-top:3px;text-align:left;font-family:var(--font-secondary), Arial, sans-serif">Professional nail care and polish</div></div></div></div></div><div style="margin-top:20px"><a href="https://book.getpagoda.com/book?salonId=e9774c5d-8e08-45bd-8170-e2b645a465a6" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="display:inline-block;background:var(--color-secondary);color:white;padding:15px 40px;border-radius:30px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;font-size:1.1rem">Book an Appointment</a></div></div></section><section class="section service-highlights-section" style="background:var(--color-secondary);color:white;text-align:center;padding:60px 20px;width:100%" data-sr-id="highlights"><div class="highlights-content" style="max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;flex-direction:row;gap:40px;align-items:center;justify-content:space-evenly;flex-wrap:wrap"><div class="highlight-item" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:20px;width:240px"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="opacity:0.9"><path d="M19.5 12.572l-7.5 7.428l-7.5-7.428a5 5 0 1 1 7.5-6.566a5 5 0 1 1 7.5 6.572"></path></svg><h2 style="font-size:20px;margin:0;color:white;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);padding-bottom:10px">Hair Styling</h2><p style="font-size:20px;line-height:1.8;opacity:0.95;margin:0">Professional hair cuts and styling</p></div><div class="highlight-item" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:20px;width:240px"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="opacity:0.9"><path d="M8 7a4 4 0 1 0 8 0a4 4 0 0 0-8 0"></path><path d="M6 21v-2a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h4a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v2"></path></svg><h2 style="font-size:20px;margin:0;color:white;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);padding-bottom:10px">Hair Coloring</h2><p style="font-size:20px;line-height:1.8;opacity:0.95;margin:0">Expert hair coloring and highlights</p></div><div class="highlight-item" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:20px;width:240px"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="opacity:0.9"><path d="M4 7v-1a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2"></path><path d="M4 17v1a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2"></path><path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1"></path><path d="M16 20h2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-1"></path><path d="M5 11h1v2h-1z"></path><path d="M10 11l0 2"></path><path d="M14 11h1v2h-1z"></path><path d="M19 11l0 2"></path></svg><h2 style="font-size:20px;margin:0;color:white;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);padding-bottom:10px">Facial Treatments</h2><p style="font-size:20px;line-height:1.8;opacity:0.95;margin:0">Rejuvenating facial treatments</p></div><div class="highlight-item" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:20px;width:240px"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="opacity:0.9"><path d="M19.5 12.572l-7.5 7.428l-7.5-7.428a5 5 0 1 1 7.5-6.566a5 5 0 1 1 7.5 6.572"></path></svg><h2 style="font-size:20px;margin:0;color:white;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);padding-bottom:10px">Nail Care</h2><p style="font-size:20px;line-height:1.8;opacity:0.95;margin:0">Professional manicures and pedicures</p></div></div></section><section class="section team-section" style="background-color:white;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;padding:60px 20px" data-sr-id="about"><div class="section-container team-container" style="max-width:992px;width:100%;margin:0 auto;text-align:center"><h2 style="font-family:var(--font-primary), serif;font-size:2.5rem;color:var(--color-primary);margin-bottom:30px">Our Team</h2><div class="team-intro rich-text-content" style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto 50px;text-align:center;font-family:var(--font-secondary), sans-serif"><p>Meet our <strong>talented</strong> professionals who are dedicated to providing you with exceptional service. Each team member brings <em>years of experience</em> and a passion for beauty.</p><p>Our team includes:</p><ul><li>Master stylists with 10+ years of experience</li><li>Certified estheticians specializing in skincare</li><li>Expert colorists trained in the latest techniques</li></ul></div><div class="team-grid" style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;gap:30px;margin-top:40px"><div class="team-member" style="background:#f8f9fa;border-radius:15px;padding:30px;text-align:center;max-width:300px;flex:0 1 calc(50% - 15px)"><div class="member-photo" style="width:150px;height:150px;border-radius:50%;margin:0 auto 20px;overflow:hidden;border:4px solid var(--color-primary)"><img src="https://example.com/staff/sarah-johnson.jpg" alt="Sarah Johnson" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover"/></div><div class="member-info"><h3 style="color:var(--color-primary);font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:10px;font-family:var(--font-primary), serif">Sarah<!-- --> <!-- -->Johnson</h3><p class="member-title" style="color:#6B7280;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:10px;font-family:var(--font-secondary), sans-serif">Master Stylist</p><p style="color:#495057;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.6">Sarah has over 15 years of experience in hair styling and color</p><div class="member-email" style="margin-top:10px"><a href="mailto:sarah@crownofbeauty.com" style="color:var(--color-primary);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.9rem">sarah@crownofbeauty.com</a></div></div></div><div class="team-member" style="background:#f8f9fa;border-radius:15px;padding:30px;text-align:center;max-width:300px;flex:0 1 calc(50% - 15px)"><div class="member-photo" style="width:150px;height:150px;border-radius:50%;margin:0 auto 20px;overflow:hidden;border:4px solid var(--color-primary)"><img src="https://example.com/staff/michael-chen.jpg" alt="Michael Chen" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover"/></div><div class="member-info"><h3 style="color:var(--color-primary);font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:10px;font-family:var(--font-primary), serif">Michael<!-- --> <!-- -->Chen</h3><p class="member-title" style="color:#6B7280;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:10px;font-family:var(--font-secondary), sans-serif">Senior Stylist</p><p style="color:#495057;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.6">Michael specializes in modern cuts and color techniques</p><div class="member-email" style="margin-top:10px"><a href="mailto:michael@crownofbeauty.com" style="color:var(--color-primary);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.9rem">michael@crownofbeauty.com</a></div></div></div><div class="team-member" style="background:#f8f9fa;border-radius:15px;padding:30px;text-align:center;max-width:300px;flex:0 1 calc(50% - 15px)"><div class="member-photo" style="width:150px;height:150px;border-radius:50%;margin:0 auto 20px;overflow:hidden;border:4px solid var(--color-primary)"><img src="https://example.com/staff/emily-rodriguez.jpg" alt="Emily Rodriguez" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover"/></div><div class="member-info"><h3 style="color:var(--color-primary);font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:10px;font-family:var(--font-primary), serif">Emily<!-- --> <!-- -->Rodriguez</h3><p class="member-title" style="color:#6B7280;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:10px;font-family:var(--font-secondary), sans-serif">Esthetician</p><p style="color:#495057;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.6">Emily provides expert facial treatments and skincare</p><div class="member-email" style="margin-top:10px"><a href="mailto:emily@crownofbeauty.com" style="color:var(--color-primary);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.9rem">emily@crownofbeauty.com</a></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section testimonials-section" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:40px;padding:50px 20px;width:100%;background:var(--color-secondary)" data-sr-id="testimonials"><div class="section-container testimonials-container" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:10px;width:100%;max-width:992px;margin:0 auto"><h2 style="font-size:32px;font-weight:700;color:white;margin-bottom:40px;text-align:center;font-family:var(--font-primary), serif">What Our Clients Say</h2><p class="testimonials-subtitle" style="font-size:1.2rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);margin-bottom:20px;font-family:var(--font-secondary), sans-serif">Read their experiences</p><div class="testimonials-intro rich-text-content" style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto 40px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.95);font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.8"><p>We value our clients' feedback and are <strong>proud</strong> of the relationships we've built. Here's what they have to say about their experience with us.</p></div><div class="testimonials-carousel" style="position:relative;width:100%;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><div class="testimonials-slides" style="position:relative;width:100%;height:300px;overflow:hidden"><div class="testimonial-slide active" data-index="0" style="position:relative;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;opacity:1"><div class="testimonial-card" style="background:white;border-top-left-radius:10px;border-top-right-radius:50px;border-bottom-left-radius:50px;border-bottom-right-radius:10px;padding:30px;text-align:center;height:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;box-shadow:0px 1px 10px 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)"><div class="testimonial-content" style="color:#495057;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:20px;font-family:var(--font-secondary), sans-serif;font-style:italic;flex-grow:1"><p>Amazing service! The staff is professional and friendly. I've been coming here for years.</p></div><div class="testimonial-author" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:15px;margin-top:20px"><img src="https://example.com/testimonials/jane-doe.jpg" alt="Jane Doe" class="author-image" style="width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;border:2px solid var(--color-secondary)"/><div class="author-info" style="text-align:left"><h4 class="testimonial-name" style="color:var(--color-primary);font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin:0;font-family:var(--font-primary), serif;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px">Jane Doe</h4><p class="testimonial-source" style="color:#6c757d;font-size:14px;margin:5px 0 0;font-style:italic">Google Reviews</p></div></div></div></div><div class="testimonial-slide" data-index="1" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;opacity:0"><div class="testimonial-card" style="background:white;border-top-left-radius:10px;border-top-right-radius:50px;border-bottom-left-radius:50px;border-bottom-right-radius:10px;padding:30px;text-align:center;height:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;box-shadow:0px 1px 10px 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)"><div class="testimonial-content" style="color:#495057;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:20px;font-family:var(--font-secondary), sans-serif;font-style:italic;flex-grow:1"><p>Best salon experience I've ever had! The attention to detail is incredible.</p></div><div class="testimonial-author" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:15px;margin-top:20px"><img src="https://example.com/testimonials/john-smith.jpg" alt="John Smith" class="author-image" style="width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;border:2px solid var(--color-secondary)"/><div class="author-info" style="text-align:left"><h4 class="testimonial-name" style="color:var(--color-primary);font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin:0;font-family:var(--font-primary), serif;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px">John Smith</h4><p class="testimonial-source" style="color:#6c757d;font-size:14px;margin:5px 0 0;font-style:italic">Yelp</p></div></div></div></div><div class="testimonial-slide" data-index="2" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;opacity:0"><div class="testimonial-card" style="background:white;border-top-left-radius:10px;border-top-right-radius:50px;border-bottom-left-radius:50px;border-bottom-right-radius:10px;padding:30px;text-align:center;height:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;box-shadow:0px 1px 10px 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)"><div class="testimonial-content" style="color:#495057;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:20px;font-family:var(--font-secondary), sans-serif;font-style:italic;flex-grow:1"><p>I love the atmosphere here. It's relaxing and the results are always perfect.</p></div><div class="testimonial-author" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:15px;margin-top:20px"><img src="https://example.com/testimonials/maria-garcia.jpg" alt="Maria Garcia" class="author-image" style="width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;border:2px solid var(--color-secondary)"/><div class="author-info" style="text-align:left"><h4 class="testimonial-name" style="color:var(--color-primary);font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin:0;font-family:var(--font-primary), serif;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px">Maria Garcia</h4><p class="testimonial-source" style="color:#6c757d;font-size:14px;margin:5px 0 0;font-style:italic">Facebook</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="carousel-dots" style="display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:12px;margin-top:30px"><button class="carousel-dot active" data-index="0" style="width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--color-primary);border:none;cursor:pointer;transform:scale(1.2)"></button><button class="carousel-dot" data-index="1" style="width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:50%;background:#ddd;border:none;cursor:pointer"></button><button class="carousel-dot" data-index="2" style="width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:50%;background:#ddd;border:none;cursor:pointer"></button></div></div></section><section class="section gallery-section" style="background-color:white;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;padding:60px 20px" data-sr-id="gallery"><div class="section-container gallery-container" style="max-width:992px;width:100%;margin:0 auto;text-align:center"><h2 style="font-family:var(--font-primary), serif;font-size:2.5rem;color:var(--color-primary);margin-bottom:40px">Photos</h2><div class="gallery-grid " style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;width:100%;max-width:992px;margin-top:40px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto"><div class="gallery-row" style="display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:stretch;width:100%"><div class="gallery-item" style="overflow:hidden;border-radius:8px;flex:1 1 calc(33.333% - 14px);min-width:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><img src="https://example.com/gallery/salon-interior.jpg" alt="Salon Interior" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block;border-radius:8px;object-fit:cover"/></div><div class="gallery-item" style="overflow:hidden;border-radius:8px;flex:1 1 calc(33.333% - 14px);min-width:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><img src="https://example.com/gallery/stylist-at-work.jpg" alt="Stylist at Work" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block;border-radius:8px;object-fit:cover"/></div><div class="gallery-item" style="overflow:hidden;border-radius:8px;flex:1 1 calc(33.333% - 14px);min-width:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><img src="https://example.com/gallery/hair-color-process.jpg" alt="Hair Color Process" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block;border-radius:8px;object-fit:cover"/></div></div><div class="gallery-row" style="display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:stretch;width:100%"><div class="gallery-item" style="overflow:hidden;border-radius:8px;flex:1 1 calc(33.333% - 14px);min-width:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><img src="https://example.com/gallery/finished-look.jpg" alt="Finished Look" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block;border-radius:8px;object-fit:cover"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section find-us-section" style="background-color:white;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;padding:60px 20px" data-sr-id="find-us"><div class="section-container find-us-container" style="max-width:992px;width:100%;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 0"><div class="find-us-content" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;align-items:start;text-align:left;gap:60px;max-width:992px;margin:0 auto"><div class="maps-column" style="background:white;border-radius:15px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)"><div class="maps-container" style="width:100%;height:100%"><iframe class="google-maps-iframe" src="https://maps.google.com/?q=Crown+of+Beauty+Salon" width="100%" height="400" style="border:0" loading="lazy" title="Google Maps Location"></iframe></div></div><div class="contact-info-column" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-start"><h2 class="find-us-title" style="font-family:var(--font-primary), serif;font-size:2.5rem;color:var(--color-primary);margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left">Call to schedule an appointment. Walk-ins are also accepted.</h2><div class="contact-details" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:30px"><div class="contact-detail-item"><h2 style="color:var(--color-primary);font-size:26px;margin-bottom:8px;font-family:var(--font-primary), serif;text-align:left">Address</h2><p style="color:#495057;font-size:20px;line-height:1.5;font-family:var(--font-secondary), sans-serif">123 Main Street, Boston, MA 02101</p></div><div class="contact-detail-item"><h2 style="color:var(--color-primary);font-size:26px;margin-bottom:8px;font-family:var(--font-primary), serif;text-align:left">Phone</h2><p style="color:#495057;font-size:20px;line-height:1.5;font-family:var(--font-secondary), sans-serif">(555) 123-4567</p></div><div class="contact-detail-item"><h2 style="color:var(--color-primary);font-size:26px;margin-bottom:8px;font-family:var(--font-primary), serif;text-align:left">Email</h2><p style="color:#495057;font-size:20px;line-height:1.5;font-family:var(--font-secondary), sans-serif"><a href="mailto:info@crownofbeauty.com" style="color:var(--color-primary);text-decoration:none">info@crownofbeauty.com</a></p></div><div class="contact-detail-item"><h2 style="color:var(--color-primary);font-si